entries.femaleVariant: Hey, hey! Take it easy! Let's talk!
Wait! Just wait a sec! Let's talk!
Why not. Curious how you're gonna be able to worm your way outta this one. You gonna tell me you didn't see that girl?
I'm listening.
Thirty seconds. Change my mind.
Fine.
Fine... but you better keep your word, else I'll have you and my iron come to an understanding.
Surprise me.
Vehicular manslaughter insurance... Hah… what a world. Think you're off the hook? That her father's OK with that? I doubt it.
entries.maleVariant: Vehicular manslaughter insurance... What a world. Think you're off the hook? That her father's OK with that? I doubt it.

entries.femaleVariant: Won't let you get away with this.
You're not going anywhere.
Hm? What the--?
I'm here to kill you.
What's there to talk about? Job's a job – nothin' personal.
No, no, no, wait! Just hear me out!
Fine. I can live with that.
You're not going anywhere.
Only place you're goin' is to the morgue.
Nobody asked her to get run over! Let's be reasonable now. I pay, you leave me alone, and I leave the city. How 'bout that, huh?
Hey, you don't have to tell me.
Someone paid you to take me out, right? Her mom, dad, fiancé, whoever.
Slow down! Waddaya mean? What girl?
The one who's blood was all over your limo.
Ohhh, that... Whoo, I thought one of my competitors sent you.
Look, this is all some gonk misunderstanding. I'm insured for "accidents" – compensation's already been paid out. Case closed.
Ah! An uninvited guest. I don't know who you are, but I know you're making a very, very big mistake.
I don't know how much they promised you, but I'm certain my safe has more. A lot more.
You let me go, everything in there is yours, and I'll transfer somewhere else in the city. Nobody, your fixer included, will have to know. It's a win-win.
Good, now fuck off. And slow down for pedestrians.
entries.maleVariant: Good. Now fuck off, and slow down for pedestrians.

entries.femaleVariant: You made a big mistake. Consequences are fatal.
You fucked up. Bad. Girl was poor, so you figured even the junkie on the corner wouldn't give two shits.
Conversation's over.
Save your breath – this convo's over. If you got any last words, now would be the time.
entries.maleVariant: Save your breath – this convo's over. If you got any last words, now'd be the time.

entries.femaleVariant: And as for this job of yours... I'm sure we can come to some kind of professional understanding.
